data.description: Nestled in the Northwood neighborhood, this residence exudes elegance and offers a blend of timeless charm and modern updates. A .26 acre lot provides for a deep house set back, boasting a delightful pool and spa, as well as a park-like yard, this home provides the perfect oasis for relaxation and entertainment. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of this meticulously maintained home. The living room features, floor to ceiling fireplace, hardwood floors, and beautiful wood-beamed ceilings that epitomize the Tudor architectural style. The stunning kitchen, which has been thoughtfully updated with contemporary finishes and top-of-the-line appliances, flows into the the window filled breakfast area. The master suite is a tranquil haven, complete with ample space, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious ensuite bathroom. The updated bathrooms throughout the home provide a perfect blend of modern convenience and classic design. Additional features include, a formal dining room with original built in buffet, study/office with original built in floor to ceiling shelves, an upstairs media/gameroom, and a two-car garage with workbench. Step outside and be captivated by the enchanting backyard with its mature trees, lush landscaping, and a serene atmosphere. Situated in a desirable neighborhood, this Tudor-style gem is conveniently located near excellent schools, military bases, and a multitude of shopping and dining options. Experience the perfect harmony of classic charm and modern comfort in this exquisite home.
